Rating: 4
Loved this for friends and for family-4 Forks! Only a few tiny changes- 1) used 4 cloves of garlic 2)used angus chuck which allowed me to cut down the beef cooking time by 1 full hour 3) in addition to the broth called for, added 1 (1.5 oz) pack of glace de veau available at fine food stores. This gave it the restaurant quality richness and it then equalled it's French cousin Beef Bourg. Cheers everyone! use good red wine- it's worth it!

